Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.14,0:55:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,view coming out of this is a hopeless world, the view of God from that level of consciousness\Nthen is that God is dead. God is dead. If we raise our level of consciousness and advance
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.49,0:55:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,in our awareness, we then move up to the level of grief. Grief. Again a negative view of\Nthe world, of ourselves. The emotions of that would be regret, loss, feeling of despondency,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.47,0:55:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,dispirited.\NA person
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.03,0:55:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,into grief holding that energy field sees this as a sad world. As they walk down the\Nstreet, a person holding this energy field sees sad, just as this person sees hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.21,0:56:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He walks down the city street, he sees the hopelessness of mankind's conditions. This\None sees the sadness. When this person looks at older people, they see how sad it is. How
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.67,0:56:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,sad it is that they are old. When they look at children, they think how sad it is when\Nthey are little kids, what these poor innocent children are going to have to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.03,0:56:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in life. When they open the newspaper, they see the sadness of all that goes on in the\Nworld, and what kind of a God would fit that sadness. A God who ignores you. Out of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.48,0:56:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the person is worthless. So, the person says. I am just a worm, and God couldn't possibly\Nhave any interest in me, if he exists at all. He would just be a God who ignores you. What
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.86,0:56:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,this energy field of fear. We see that we are the creator now of that. We are the owner. We are the\Nsource. The emotions of worry, anxiety, and panic. The deflation of self-esteem. And to them, this is
