Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.57,0:57:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,nightmare. So this world is an endless nightmare. The creator of such a nightmare is a very punitive\Ngod. Because of revenge, because of retaliation, we'll move up into retaliation. He becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.61,0:57:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the punisher. As we move up into desire, the solar\Nplexus, craving, what makes Sammy run, wantingness. There's no satisfying that, is there? No matter what
