Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.01,1:04:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,expand, to explore. If there is such a God, if there is a God, it's okay with me. And if there\Nisn't okay with me, there's sort of an inner sense of fairness about. If there is a God, he'll be
